            </b>11-14 July 2011 - PRAGUE<br>
            This is the first call for the 8th EFITA conference that will
be held=20
            from 11th to 14th July 2011 at the campus site of the Czech
University=20
            of Life Sciences Prague, in a beautiful landlocked country in
the=20
            heart of Europe, in the Czech Republic. This letter is to
brief you=20
            on the most important organizational aspects of the
forthcoming conference.<br>
            This conference is co-organized with the 8th ECPA, the 5th
ECPLF conferences=20
            as there is an established tradition of bringing EFITA, ECPA
and ECPLF=20
            together.<br>
